---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Alexander's Personal Site"
  description="Learn more about Alexander, a software developer specializing in web technologies."
>
  <section class="py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg">
          Hello! I'm Alexander, a passionate software developer with a focus on creating 
          clean, efficient, and user-friendly web applications.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          With expertise in modern web technologies, I enjoy building everything from small 
          business websites to rich interactive web applications. My approach combines technical 
          excellence with an eye for design and user experience.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8">My Skills</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Frontend</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
              <li>HTML/CSS/JavaScript</li>
              <li>React/Vue/Svelte</li>
              <li>TailwindCSS</li>
              <li>Next.js/Astro</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Backend</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
              <li>Node.js</li>
              <li>Python</li>
              <li>REST APIs</li>
              <li>Database Design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8">My Journey</h2>
        
        <p>
          I started my coding journey back in [year]. Since then, I've worked on numerous projects, 
          constantly expanding my skills and keeping up with the ever-evolving tech landscape.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          When I'm not coding, you can find me [hobbies/interests]. I believe in continuous learning 
          and enjoy sharing my knowledge through my blog and open-source contributions.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <div class="sticky top-10">
          <div class="bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 h-72 mb-6 rounded-lg"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Location</h3>
            <p>Amsterdam, Netherlands</p>
            
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg pt-2">Education</h3>
            <p>BSc in Computer Science</p>
            <p>University of Example</p>
            
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg pt-2">Languages</h3>
            <p>English (Fluent)</p>
            <p>Dutch (Native)</p>
            
            <div class="pt-6">
              <a 
                href="/contact" 
                class="block w-full py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-center rounded-md transition-colors"
              >
                Get in Touch
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>